{
  "texts": [
    "In recent years, transformer-based methods have been widely proposed.",
    "Anomaly-Transformer [51] detect anomalies by comparing Kullback-Leible (KL) divergence between two distributions.",
    "Some methods [48,60] have begun to solve some practical problems from the frequency domain.",
    "Moerover, many transfer learning methods have been proposed [12,27,54,55].",
    "Our paper presents a novel unsupervised method for detecting anomalies in UTS, termed FCVAE."
  ]
}